--------- Tracks -----------

03 1983...(A Mermaid I should Turn To Be)

This is marvellous CD: a Hendrix tribute which works because Nigel Kennedy and a very talented group take the spirit of Hendrix and improvise on it, rather than just try to reproduce his songs note for note.
